Computerized Services

In Line with its commitment to Citizen Friendly Services, the Transport Department has enabled Help Desks at all its Transport offices to help the visiting customers with the procedures and correct forms and basic requirements to carry out a transaction at the transport office.  The help desk also reduces the menace of touts and unauthorized persons to exploit the hapless customers.  Any customer is welcome to seek the assistance of the help desk.
