Help Desk at RTO Offices
Computerized Services

To facilitate the customer and to minimise his wastage of time by standing in long cues, the Transport Department has introduced the slot booking facility for learning licence test.  All customers who want to take a learner licence test now will have to first book a slot based on their convenience and can make payment online either through a credit card or a netbanking account or any e-Seva center or any RTO office.  Come at the appointed time and produce the orginal documents to the RTO personnel and get set on taking the test.  Waiting in long queues is a thing of the past!
