No person will drive any Motor Vehicle and no owner of Motor Vehicle will cause or permit the vehicle to be driven in any public place or any other place, unless the vehicle is registered.  The registration number is generated by the system in alphabetical order as per the applicants name, however owner may apply for reservation of special number.
a)
